00:11:31.270 --> 00:11:33.910
And so I think it's amazing,
because most people have

00:11:33.910 --> 00:11:36.840
no idea that these patterns are
built into barcodes and things

00:11:36.840 --> 00:11:37.385
around them.

00:11:37.385 --> 00:11:39.051
And so actually if
you look on the book,

00:11:39.051 --> 00:11:42.550
it's got the barcode at the
bottom and the ISBN at the top.

00:11:42.550 --> 00:11:45.380
And the ISBN is a subtly
different pattern.

00:11:45.380 --> 00:11:47.180
But again, it's got
exactly the same thing.

00:11:47.180 --> 00:11:48.970
Credit cards have
the same thing.

00:11:48.970 --> 00:11:51.150
I can do the same stunt
