Best name of a theory ever.

00:18:31.470 --> 00:18:34.610
And so people are
know theorists.

00:18:34.610 --> 00:18:35.930
Are you a theorist?

00:18:35.930 --> 00:18:37.490
I am knot theorist.

00:18:37.490 --> 00:18:40.690
So knot theorists look at the
maths behind different knots.

00:18:40.690 --> 00:18:43.670
And as humans we know
dangerously little about knots.

00:18:43.670 --> 00:18:46.240
It's a reasonably new
area of mathematics.

00:18:46.240 --> 00:18:48.750
Well, it kicked
off in the 1800s.

00:18:48.750 --> 00:18:52.460
But today we still haven't got
a great understanding of knots,

00:18:52.460 --> 00:18:53.190
in general.

00:18:53.190 --> 00:18:56.250
And, in fact, I put a picture
of one knot in my book.

00:18:56.250 --> 00:18:57.500
I've got a shot of it up here.

00:18:57.500 --> 00:19:01.030
We still do not know the
best way to undo this knot.

00:19:01.030 --> 00:19:02.720
This is called the
1011 knot if you

00:19:02.720 --> 00:19:04.200
want to look it up afterwards.

00:19:04.200 --> 00:19:07.360
And when you do a
knot diagram, you

00:19:07.360 --> 00:19:09.080
leave a gap when
it goes underneath.

00:19:09.080 --> 00:19:11.300
These are not just
joint bits of string.

00:19:11.300 --> 00:19:13.370
This is where it goes
underneath there.

00:19:13.370 --> 00:19:14.980
And to undo a knot
mathematically,

00:19:14.980 --> 00:19:16.910
you do sort of a
crossing switch.

00:19:16.910 --> 00:19:18.641
So you would cut one
bit of the string,

00:19:18.641 --> 00:19:20.890
move it around another one,
and join it back up again.

00:19:20.890 --> 00:19:23.870
So you take it from one side to
the other side and rejoin it.

00:19:23.870 --> 00:19:28.180
And we know this not can
be undone in three crossing

00:19:28.180 --> 00:19:32.180
switches, but no one's
found a way to do it in two,

00:19:32.180 --> 00:19:35.510
and likewise, know one's managed
to prove that there isn't a way

00:19:35.510 --> 00:19:37.034
to do it in two.

00:19:37.034 --> 00:19:38.700
This is an open
question in mathematics.

00:19:38.700 --> 00:19:41.050
This is, in fact,
the most simple knot

00:19:41.050 --> 00:19:42.850
for which we do not understand.

00:19:42.850 --> 00:19:46.110
At for the vast majority of
knots above it we have no idea.

00:19:46.110 --> 00:19:50.230
And so my theory is, if enough
people make this out of string

00:19:50.230 --> 00:19:53.050
and try it, sooner
or later, if there's

00:19:53.050 --> 00:19:56.510
a way to do it-- for a very
generous definition of sooner

00:19:56.510 --> 00:20:00.060
or later possibly-- we will come
across how it can be undone.

00:20:00.060 --> 00:20:02.350
And at that point fame
and mathematical fortune

00:20:02.350 --> 00:20:07.374
is yours, for a very narrow
definition of fame and fortune.

00:20:07.374 --> 00:20:09.540
So, dude if you can try and
make that out of string,

00:20:09.540 --> 00:20:10.100
you look it up online.

00:20:10.100 --> 00:20:11.170
It's the 1011 knot.

00:20:11.170 --> 00:20:12.920
If you do find a way
to do it let me know.

00:20:12.920 --> 00:20:14.870
Photograph yourself
