00:20:14.870 --> 00:20:16.690
where you're going to make
the crossing switches first.

00:20:16.690 --> 00:20:17.315
Then make them.

00:20:17.315 --> 00:20:19.450
If it untangles, we'll
know what you actually did.

00:20:19.450 --> 00:20:20.908
Because if it
happens and you don't

00:20:20.908 --> 00:20:23.510
know how it was arranged--
because in this arrangement

00:20:23.510 --> 00:20:24.209
it won't work.

